Manage playgrounds, test cases, and experiments

Usage:
  agentclash playground [command]

Aliases:
  playground, pg

Available Commands:
  create      Create a playground
  delete      Delete a playground
  experiment  Manage playground experiments
  get         Get a playground
  list        List playgrounds
  test-case   Manage playground test cases
  update      Update a playground

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for playground

Global Flags:
      --api-url string     API base URL (overrides config)
      --json               Output in JSON format
      --no-color           Disable color output
      --non-interactive    Disable interactive prompts (also honored: CI=true, AGENTCLASH_NON_INTERACTIVE=1, --json, no TTY)
  -o, --output string      Output format: table, json, yaml
  -q, --quiet              Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose            Enable debug output on stderr
  -w, --workspace string   Workspace ID (overrides config)
      --yes                Skip confirmation prompts

Use "agentclash playground [command] --help" for more information about a command.
